title: Donaldson leaves playoff game after taking knee to head
text:
> Texas Donaldson leaves playoff game after taking knee to head Toronto Blue Jays' Josh Donaldson (20) breaks up a double play under Texas Rangers second baseman Rougned Odor during the fourth inning of Game 1 of the American League Division Series in Toronto on Thursday, Oct. 8, 2015. (Frank Gunn/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
